commit.message:
Update docs and bump minor release

  - Clean facets module

Refactor XsdList on item_type

  - Replace base_type with item_type in XsdList: remove ambiguity
    when restrict a list type that has constraints (facets)
  - This fix issue #396
Move root_type property implementation to effective types
Add tests for download_schemas()

Refactor match_locations() and the logged() decorator

  - More precise match of locations (exclude incompatible ones, use
    a glob pattern derived from location path and PurePath.match)
  - The logged decorator do not remove loglevel argument anymore

Forbid http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/ as targetNamespace

  - Move schema export tests to test_exports.py

Add download_schemas() to package API

  - The new API downloads XSD schemas from local or remote
    resources, storing them in a target directory;
  - This is an alternative to schema export, that can save
    a complete set of connected schema resources;
  - Option to not modify the original schemas, using a saved
    location map instead (see uri_mapper option for schemas).

Refactoring of export_schema()

  - Add SchemaSource dataclass
  - Add save_schema_sources()
Add type annotations for meta_schema in XMLSchema10/11 classes
Remove deprecated classmethod check_schema()
Bump minor release

Merge PR #393 and fix CLI broken tests

  - Fix: residuals_filter() in exports.py module

CLI: Use stdout and stderr to print Messages with xmlschema-validate command (#393)

* feat(cli-validate): Use stdout and stderr instead of print statement

This change helps users to distinguish between error messages and
others, e.g. in CI pipelines.

Signed-off-by: Sven Sager <s.sager@kunbus.com>

* feat(cli-validate): Use argument -v to print errors on stderr

The argument -v (verbosity) is not yet used in the validate function.
The specification of -v is now used in xmlschema-validate to obtain a
detailed error report on the stderr. This helps users to find the error
in their XML files at the mentioned place.

Signed-off-by: Sven Sager <s.sager@kunbus.com>

---------

Signed-off-by: Sven Sager <s.sager@kunbus.com>

commit.message: Update requirements and CI tests configuration

Fix schema export (issue #387)

  - Fix the replacement pattern in export_schema()
  - Add loglevel argument, apply with a decorator
  - Add logger.debug statements
  - Don't remove non-remote residuals schemaLocation entries
Add logging helper functions: a set level helper and a decorator
Minimize typing cast to elementpath.protocols
Add schema lazy properties reset in XMLSchemaBase.clear()
Merge extended annotations parsing from v3.1.0 develop

Complete GData converter (issue #388)

  - Derived from default converter: there are differences with
    BadgerFish converter that advice to split the code to avoid
    complications
  - Rename converter class as GDataConverter
  - Add XMLSchemaAssertPathWarning to package API
Add GDataConverter prototype
Remove custom protocols, use elementpath.protocols instead
Extend protocols tests
